{"number":22,"verseCount":4,"verses":[[1,["Behold, I say unto you that all ",["old",["study-note-ref","a",[["Heb. 8:13","nt/heb/8.13"],"; ",["3 Ne. 9:17","bofm/3-ne/9.17"],"; ",["12:47 (46–47)","bofm/3-ne/12.47"],"."]]]," covenants have I caused to be done away in this thing; and this is a ",["new",["study-note-ref","b",[["D&C 66:2","dc-testament/dc/66.2"],". ",["TG New and Everlasting Covenant","tg/new-and-everlasting-covenant"],"."]]]," and an everlasting ",["covenant",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Covenants","tg/covenants"],"."]]],", even that which was from the beginning."]],[2,["Wherefore, although a man should be baptized an hundred times it availeth him nothing, for you cannot enter in at the strait gate by the ",["law",["study-note-ref","a",[["Gal. 2:16","nt/gal/2.16"],". ",["TG Law of Moses","tg/law-of-moses"],"."]]]," of Moses, neither by your ",["dead works",["study-note-ref","b",[["Moro. 8:23 (23–26)","bofm/moro/8.23"],"."]]],"."]],[3,["For it is because of your dead works that I have caused this last covenant and this church to be built up unto me, even as in days of old."]],[4,["Wherefore, enter ye in at the ",["gate",["study-note-ref","a",[["Matt. 7:13 (13–14)","nt/matt/7.13"],"; ",["Luke 13:24","nt/luke/13.24"],"; ",["2 Ne. 9:41","bofm/2-ne/9.41"],"; ",["31:9 (9, 17–18)","bofm/2-ne/31.9"],"; ",["3 Ne. 14:14 (13–14)","bofm/3-ne/14.14"],"; ",["27:33","bofm/3-ne/27.33"],"; ",["D&C 43:7","dc-testament/dc/43.7"],". ",["TG Baptism, Essential","tg/baptism-essential"],"."]]],", as I have commanded, and ",["seek",["study-note-ref","b",[["Rom. 11:34","nt/rom/11.34"],"; ",["1 Cor. 2:16","nt/1-cor/2.16"],"; ",["Jacob 4:10","bofm/jacob/4.10"],"."]]]," not to counsel your God. Amen."]]],"volume":"dc"}